How to write jenkins file?
==========================
pipeline(){

agent <server>

stages
  stage
    steps
    steps
    steps
  stage
    steps
    steps
}

pipeline {
    agent any

    stages {
        stage('Hello') {
            steps {
                echo 'Hello World'
            }
        }
        stage('Hi') {
            steps {
                echo 'Hello World'
            }
        }
        stage('Bye') {
            steps {
                echo 'Hello World'
            }
        }
    }
}


Red: Fail
Green: Pass
Yellow: unstable

